es.',1),(22,'EXIT','LIKERT','I can see the benefit of biomimicry to a range of careers and further study.',2),(23,'EXIT','LIKERT','I can identify and assess my own and team’s strengths and weaknesses.',3),(24,'EXIT','LIKERT','I am more motivated to create positive changes through sustainable innovation.',4),(25,'EXIT','LIKERT','I feel connected with nature as a source of inspiration for solutions to human challenges.',5),(26,'EXIT','LIKERT','I feel a greater sense of a being part of nature.',6),(27,'EXIT','LIKERT','I feel confident to collaborate with teams from other countries to solve sustainability issues.',7),(28,'EXIT','LIKERT','I can imagine a desirable future and link this with practical design ideas.',8);
